title: For Sale:  chinese norinco sks, 2 mags, 1100rds ammo+mag catch mod
postcontent: matching numbers chinese sks in excellent condition. barely ever shot, like new internally, wood stock in very good condition with a few handling marks, barrel and gun metal blue are 100%. custom modification to magazine catch lever on bottom of trigger assembly. if you are familiar with these rifles, you know they origionally come with a fixed mag and you have to load ammo from the top. you can convert the sks  to detachable aftermarket "duckbill mags" but the conversion leaves the mag extremely loose (specs vary depending on magazine mfg.), and prone to malfunction or fall out during operation. this problem is due to the mag catch lever not being able to  engage as far as it needs to. well, i fixed that problem, and both mags lock up tight resulting in flawless operation. i googled and utubed this mod and there isnt another one like it that i can find (pat on the back) and it looks stock, unlike other mods i did find online. in pic 3, the worn spot behind the mag catch lever is where the mag catch was origionally seated, as you can see, the mag catch is moved foward 3/8" to 1/2" resulting in longer catch spring travel, and will now engage any mfg "duckbill" mag firmly.  comes with 2 detachable mags and 1100rds wolf ammo. $950 nine18nine022583 jeff.
